subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick, who will make her Nascar Sprint Cup debut in Sunday’s Daytona 500, crashed hard into an inside wall Thursday on the final lap of a qualifying race.
